About.Name: Sesen Yonas
About.AboutText: I am a computer science student at Seattle Pacific University, focused on software development and programming, especially in C++. I love taking on challenging projects and working with others to learn and share knowledge. Outside of class, I participate in hackathons, coding competitions, and open-source projects. I believe in continuous learning and always look for new technologies and methods to explore.
